eizoen 2 aflevering 03: "Real Dead Housewife of Seattle"
Liv eats the brains of a recently murdered trophy wife who was pushed to her death from the balcony of her stunning
architectural home in the hills by a hired hit man. A Pinot Grigio-sipping, suddenly fashion obsessed Liv and 
Detective Babineaux begin questioning suspects in their search for the original brains behind this murder. 
Meanwhile, Liv and Ravi are surprised to learn that Peyton has returned to Seattle.
